由于黄河的一些地理及氣候的先天性原因（如凌汛等），虽然是中国第二大河，但黄河的航运能力有限，目前仅实现局部河段季节通航。而黄河的全河段通航也在规划中<ref>{{cite news | language = zh-cn | author = 严冰 沈荫梾 杨帆 郭肖杰 | coauthors =  | url = http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrbhwb/html/2009-09/22/content_347922.htm | title = 黄河何时能通航？ | work =  | publisher = 人民日报海外版 | pages =  | date =  | accessdate = 2009-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091001221322/http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrbhwb/html/2009-09/22/content_347922.htm | archive-date = 2009-10-01 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

